HEADWORD: Tesla transformer
<hw>Tes"la trans*form"er</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[After N. <etsep>Tesla</etsep>, American
electrician.]</ety> <fld>(Elec.)</fld> <def>A transformer without iron,
